### Get User All
GET {{BaseURL}}/user/information HTTP/1.1
content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get User By Username
GET {{BaseURL}}/user/nonuser/information HTTP/1.1
content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

